Better Me
Being a better person, starts with baby steps. Alexa will suggest task from Jonathan Duhon that you can complete to uplift your soul. 
We have to intentionally do things that enhance our life. These task are small and easy to do. 

Better Me Please is part of The Me Collection by Jonathan Duhon
